The evidence with the title 'Bill Clinton: Gingrich opposed bill that led to balanced budgets ... ' says Dec 20, 2011  ... It 's a claim that has been central to Newt Gingrich's presidential campaign: that he “ balanced the budget for four straight years ” when he was speaker of the U.S.  ... They examined Gingrich 's claim that, “ for four years, we balanced the budget and paid off $405 billion in debt, ” and declared the statement false. 
